                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/14775.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Brazilian Minister to
                                    Mexico</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Brazilian Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Mexico City</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-04-03">
                                    <hi rend="italic">April 3, 1915</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>482. Your 599, March 30, 6 p.m. Thanks for your information and kind
                            words in last part.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Cardoso de Oliveira.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
